idylfin
=======

Quantitative Finance Library for Java by Idylwood Technologies

Features:
Pure Java implementation
High performant, accurate numerics library
Thread safe design
Clean API
Lightweight

Sharpe Ratio and other financial statistics
Split and dividend adjustment

Dependencies:
IdylFin currently depends on Apache Commons Math, Jsoup and GRAL, forks of which are included in this source tree. In future versions I hope to get rid of the dependencies.

